msgstr "Rento pallopeli"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.kollision.appdata.xml:17
msgid ""
"Kollision is a casual game where you need to throw your ball and avoid the "
"others balls on the table as long as possible."
msgstr ""
"Kollision on rento peli, jossa heität palloa ja yrität vältellä toisten "
"palloja laudalla niin pitkään kuin mahdollista."
